N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.29 - Withdrawal of petition or other pleading

State Regulations
A party may withdraw a petition or other pleading at any
time by notifying the Board in writing with a copy to all other parties to the
proceeding. Notes
